::Cygnar::
       He lands outside of Galvatron's base transforming back into his robot 
mode.  He calmly walks inside.  "Sir, I have excellent news.  The Maximals 
have agreed to stay out of any conflict between the Predacons and the 
Tripreds.  The only condition Rodimus Prime demanded was that you and him 
would fight to the death at some undefined time in the future.  I didn't 
foresee any problem there."

--part1_12b.15b4c239.2a8aadfe_boundary
